title: Grateful Dead Live at Boston Garden on 1993-09-28
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Gray, Greatest Story Ever Told, Row Jimmy, Minglewood Blues, So Many Roads, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Bird Song

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Samson & Delilah-> Uncle John's Band-> Playin' In The Band-> Drums-> Attics-> Throwing Stones-> Good Lovin E: US Blues
